description: Enjoi Sweets Truck is serving up delicious desserts in Tampa! Their real butter- real sugar frosting is literally the icing on the cake here! Their cupcake menu rotates daily (check their schedule!) and includes everything from traditional favorites like Red Velvet and Vanilla to concoctions like Cinnamon Roll and Black Bottom Banana. Don't forget to check out Enjoi Sweet's pies and cookies as well! All items can be ordered by the dozen, so Treat yo Self!
name: Enjoi Sweets
